channel.title: Devolution - Putting Delta in the past
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/28vu5ug.jpg[/img] [B][U]Welcome to Devolution.[/U][/B]
I am Josh. Anybody wanna try and start shit here because I'm posting a good server with a low post count, is going to get taken out by my superiority over the fool.
Devolution = Dodian R.I.P
Dodian was Shut Down Devolution 1.2.6 was passed on from Bakatool Killamess to be continued. Devolution 2.7 was released by Killamess when he quit RSPS Bakatool Returned Bakatool and I started working on "Devolution Dodian reincarnated" Bakatool Quit again, he realized he should have stayed out the first time I Continue the name, on behalf of Bakatool and Killamess, I Am known as Flash and Owner-Josh, or Ambitious on various communities.
[COLOR=RoyalBlue]BETA Download[/COLOR] - [url=http://runepalace.net/download]http://runepalace.net/download[/url]
Latest Update: So BETA is boring, we know. Version 1 is coming soon, with Tutorial island, shops, an economy, and a few skills have been added. We will then begin advertising, and the staff will be working on Minigames and combat more to make sure it's all fun and games. We currently do not have any minigames to 100% but I plan to release basic ones and work off them, because you start at te bottom, not the top.
[b]Here is a sample of Tutorial island.[/b]
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/eez9e.gif[/img]
Actual Progress log [COLOR=Red]++++++++[/COLOR][COLOR=Lime]++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++[/COLOR]
This Server/Client is nowhere near finished, or ready to be known as an actual server. At the moment all you can do is fight and spawn.
over the next few weeks I will be adding in the "Serverly Touches" to make it ready for the official release. Thanks for viewing, comments/feedback.
[COLOR=red]Note:[/COLOR] I am currently looking for one other programmer [Server Sided] I do most of the client work, and much Server sided but need a helping hand.
__ -- Devolution -- __ Server Base: Dev 1.1 {Located [url=http://runepalace.net/showthread.php?101-Devolution-1-1-Official-Release-Loading-377-cache-%7C%7C-317-Deob-client]Here[/url]} Client Base: Bluur
Devolution 1.0 *Graham's event manager *Clean flax picking *loaded 377 cache to #317 release client. [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2a9s0vq.jpg[/img]
[SPOILER="V1.0.1"] *Clean 420 Sideicons *Old Spec Bar *Whip Emote *New NPC's global *Fixed up woodcutting a small bit [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2di3hia.jpg[/img]
Dev 1.1.1 - 377 Gameframe * clean 377 gameframe added * Model preloading {parsing} * Anti Xlog *Anti Dupe * Cannot trade,fight,or drop trade yourself * 2 shops added * Buy "x" * Faster DDS * Cleaned Autospawn again. * Cannot hit more than max HP [Example: Cannot hit more than 22 on a guard] * Small Combat Video - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHw2-elK8SI]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHw2-elK8SI[/url] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/148m3o4.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/30bns6g.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/8wijvp.jpg[/img]
1.1.2 Lookin healthy * added RS2 HP Bar * New magic system * Multi PK Tele * Tutorial Island * 70% Fishing,woodcutting,theiving {simple} * 508 Textures * 508 Bank Interfaces * New player stance * SWAT's Extending Emote & Graphics list * Godwars bosses and minibosses added * Small jFrame * Bluur's Cursors * Dragon Claws * Dragon Claws Emote * Godsword stance * RS2 Vengance * Piety * 474 Gameframe added * fixed trees {removed black areas with 508 textures} * HD Dragon Platebody * Varrock Armor * Fixed Whip emote {attacking only for now, animating the whip model myself later} * Godwars emotes * Falador Home Base * working on making it a "player friendly" Server * Most 474 items * Release BETA Download - 24% complete server, but people wanted it. * A small video - [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFEn6yKz5uk]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFEn6yKz5uk[/url] [IMG]http://www.gifninja.com/Workspace/33d7ad91-d210-4d29-83dc-e6fb78ae59a7/output.gif[/img] [IMG]http://www.gifninja.com/Workspace/cd77f8b1-404d-42cf-9158-f1edfd75268f/output.gif[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2q3sv1k.jpg[/img]
* [Clipped] Following in a handler {tested on players, not yet NPC's as i had none at the time.} * Slayer Tower * Shops * Economy based NPCDrop's * to be continued... {1.1.3 still in progress}
Soon to come - - Barbarian Assult - Fight caves - Fightpits - Pk Loot {I'm hoping to do this, having troubles so far} - Random Events - Quests - Webclient - Godwars dungeons using proper mapdata {I'm hoping to do this} - Fist of Guthix {sounds cool, need to see what it's really like on RS first} - 21 skills - More HD Textures - Clan chat
More Media - sorry it's blue, GIFninja
